Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.12,0:00:15.74,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Step aside, Kotarou-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.30,0:00:17.24,Default,K,0,0,0,,Kotori...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.76,0:00:21.12,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,If Salvation comes to pass, \Nthe Key will return to the planet,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.12,0:00:23.42,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,and I'll lose my druid powers.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.42,0:00:24.75,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,And if that happens...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.18,0:00:30.03,Default,K,0,0,0,,Because I'm probably a daemon \Nwho's only alive thanks to your powers,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.03,0:00:30.76,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'll die?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.09,0:00:33.31,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to bear that.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.31,0:00:36.76,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,You're the only hope I have left in this world!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.15,0:00:39.27,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.27,0:00:43.08,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Druids have ways to prevent the Key \Nfrom returning to the planet, even if it dies.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.08,0:00:46.02,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,So I won't let you be erased.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.02,0:00:47.52,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'll prove it to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.96,0:00:49.77,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Prove...?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.08,0:00:54.08,Default,K,0,0,0,,If I really were a daemon,\N I wouldn't be able to defy my master.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.08,0:00:57.78,Default,K,0,0,0,,So I'll go against your wishes to prove that I'm not.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.78,0:00:59.95,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,My wishes?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.95,0:01:03.29,Default,K,0,0,0,,You want to get away from all \Nthis Key and druid stuff, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.74,0:01:05.49,Default,K,0,0,0,,I won't let you.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.49,0:01:08.79,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'll force you to make the most difficult choice.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.54,0:01:11.42,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Are you saying I should continue to suffer?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.42,0:01:12.40,Default,K,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.40,0:01:14.05,Default,K,0,0,0,,Because I'm not a daemon.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.92,0:01:16.93,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm Tennouji Kotarou, the person.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.62,0:01:18.50,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,No you're not!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.50,0:01:20.12,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,You are a daemon!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.12,0:01:24.27,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,The Kotarou-kun I knew wasn't cheerful at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.27,0:01:26.88,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,He was moody, unsociable,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.88,0:01:29.85,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,cold, not nice at all...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.75,0:01:34.50,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,and he didn't save me!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.45,0:01:37.95,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,You're a daemon.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.50,0:01:40.48,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,One created by my desires,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.95,0:01:43.50,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,given the kind of personality I wanted.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.86,0:01:45.46,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,A daemon...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.54,0:01:48.02,Default,K,0,0,0,,Say, Kotori.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.02,0:01:51.52,Default,K,0,0,0,,The Key must've been \Na huge burden on you, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.52,0:01:52.46,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.93,0:01:55.06,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'll fight your weakness.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.42,0:01:58.58,Default,K,0,0,0,,If you're gonna waver from your duty,\N then I'll protect the Key.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.58,0:01:59.54,Default,K,0,0,0,,So please...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.47,Default,K,0,0,0,,Let's stay together until the very end.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.28,0:02:08.94,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,You really aren't nice at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.41,0:02:21.88,Default,K,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.88,0:02:22.92,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.92,0:02:24.71,Default,K,0,0,0,,What is Salvation?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.14,0:02:27.41,Default,K,0,0,0,,Is it something that'll make\N the world a better place?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.74,0:02:28.54,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,It's ruin.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.71,0:02:40.44,Default,K,0,0,0,,Kaga—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.93,0:02:49.15,Default,K,0,0,0,,Shizuru?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.15,0:02:50.44,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Kotarou-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.44,0:02:51.44,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,The Key...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.94,0:03:10.83,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,Kotarou...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.08,0:03:14.59,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,Proof...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.10,0:03:17.73,Default,K,0,0,0,,Proof... Proof?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.73,0:03:19.84,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you mean by "proof"?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.49,0:03:21.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.30,0:03:23.13,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.67,0:03:25.48,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.20,0:03:36.46,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.24,0:03:37.98,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,But where?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.37,0:03:41.24,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,A hill?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.78,0:03:43.14,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.52,0:03:44.99,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,That hill.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.23,0:04:30.56,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have this faint inkling
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.12,0:04:34.75,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}that a myriad of times that aren't now \Nand countless places that aren't here
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.50,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}came together to form this one night.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.84,0:04:40.34,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'm positive I'll find her there.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.02,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Her"?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.02,0:04:43.54,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who's that supposed to be?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.74,0:04:51.64,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hey, you th—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.37,0:05:17.50,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is as far as I get tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.60,0:05:28.14,Default,K,0,0,0,,Get going, Shizuru.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.14,0:05:31.75,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do without you?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.52,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I won't have anything left!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.95,0:05:45.53,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,The look on your face is saying it'll be all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.53,0:05:48.02,Default,K,0,0,0,,I can change.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.02,0:05:50.92,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'll change so much, \Nno destruction or whatever will beat me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.28,0:05:53.54,Default,K,0,0,0,,And I'll be waiting for you, right here.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.73,0:05:55.41,Default,Sh,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.41,0:05:57.16,Default,Sh,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.16,0:05:58.29,Default,Sh,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.67,0:05:59.79,Default,K,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.79,0:06:03.42,Default,K,0,0,0,,You'll always have a place in my heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.42,0:06:06.60,Default,K,0,0,0,,So please find me,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.60,0:06:09.06,Default,K,0,0,0,,even if I go a little overboard \Nwith the changes, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.06,0:06:10.17,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Kotarou...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.17,0:06:11.68,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Kotarou!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.19,0:06:13.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,If only time would...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.72,0:06:16.94,Default,K,0,0,0,,We should hurry.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.69,0:06:21.32,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.32,0:06:25.08,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I love you more than anyone or anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.08,0:06:26.93,Default,K,0,0,0,,I feel the same, Shizuru.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.49,0:06:28.34,Default,K,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.08,0:06:35.01,Default,K,0,0,0,,Let's meet again...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.58,0:06:38.16,Default,K,0,0,0,,next time.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.09,Default,K,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.94,0:07:08.95,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to say, this is quite the pleasant night.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.45,0:07:14.95,Default,K,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.59,0:07:26.59,Default,K,0,0,0,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.67,0:07:33.84,Default,K,0,0,0,,Aren't you lonely staying here all by yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.27,0:07:36.97,Default,K,0,0,0,,Don't you wanna talk to someone once in a while?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.15,0:07:44.14,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm Tennouji Kotarou.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.14,0:07:47.11,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'd prefer if you'd just call me Kotarou.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.66,Default,K,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.66,0:07:49.79,Default,K,0,0,0,,If you don't mind,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.79,0:07:52.11,Default,K,0,0,0,,could we kill some time with a friendly chat?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.33,Default,K,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.33,0:07:55.10,Default,K,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.10,0:07:56.79,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, I know! Homework, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.79,0:07:58.12,Default,K,0,0,0,,Okay, let me help—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.79,Default,K,0,0,0,,Is that my...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.89,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,It's really lively here.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.89,Default,K,0,0,0,,Well, the Harvest Festa {\i1}is{\i0} coming up.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.89,0:08:23.24,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,The Harvest Festa?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.24,0:08:26.11,Default,K,0,0,0,,Wanna go together?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.96,0:08:29.76,Default,K,0,0,0,,The mess with the Gaia \Nextremists has been cleared up.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.76,0:08:32.15,Default,K,0,0,0,,Surely we can take some time off to relax.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.97,0:08:34.53,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.42,0:08:38.16,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn, my girlfriend is a total cutie!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.97,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,What's that over there?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.30,0:08:45.42,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hey, Chihaya!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.92,0:08:49.67,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,There sure is a lot of stuff here.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.28,0:08:54.48,Default,K,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.48,0:08:55.43,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'll take this one.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.68,0:08:59.94,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,You like it?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.94,0:09:01.93,Default,K,0,0,0,,W-Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.02,0:09:07.21,Default,K,0,0,0,,Like it?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.21,0:09:09.85,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,I can't see it clearly enough to answer.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.94,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,But I guess it's kind of cute.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.94,0:09:16.07,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, good. I thought it'd look great on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.08,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,C-Can I really have it?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.08,0:09:21.25,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah. To commemorate our first date.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.90,0:09:23.95,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.28,0:09:32.34,Default,K,0,0,0,,You're taking it off?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.68,0:09:35.22,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,I can't see it well when I'm wearing it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.22,0:09:38.02,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,And it's kind of embarrassing...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.02,0:09:39.56,Default,K,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.56,0:09:41.56,Default,K,0,0,0,,But hey, that's how it usually goes.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.56,0:09:43.35,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,I-I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.82,0:09:46.94,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hey! Now I can't even see it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.94,0:09:49.86,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,What's the problem? At least I'm wearing it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.86,0:09:52.36,Default,K,0,0,0,,C'mon, gimme a little peek.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.36,0:09:55.36,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Oh, fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.91,Default,K,0,0,0,,Nice, I see 'em.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.88,0:10:08.25,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories are at their clearest\N just before I wake up.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.84,0:10:10.25,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}Over and over and over,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.25,0:10:13.50,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}I try to talk to the girl, get killed,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.60,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}and dream about my memories.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.26,0:10:19.83,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}In one such memory,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.83,0:10:22.26,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a family with Kotori.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.20,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was bliss.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.20,0:10:25.27,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}However...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.27,0:10:26.22,Default,All,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.22,0:10:27.79,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}In another memory...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.79,0:10:31.91,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\an8}And this guy was like, \N"I'll flatten you and drown your rotten corpse!"
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.91,0:10:33.91,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\an8}Really? That guy sounds like such a riot!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.91,0:10:34.78,Default,Mi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd somehow gotten to know an OL living in Setagaya,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.78,0:10:37.37,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hamada Michiko-san, and married her.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.78,0:10:41.73,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}And in another, me and Akane-san,\N {\i0}Akane-san{\i1} of all people,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.73,0:10:44.66,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}were in an adult relationship.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.42,0:10:48.29,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}I also found myself in a paradise \Nbeyond my wildest dreams!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.72,0:10:50.94,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, she's dynamite by herself,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.92,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}but there were {\i0}two{\i1} of her! {\i0}Two of her{\i1}!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.67,0:10:57.15,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}The ruin of civilization.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.80,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gaia's remnants.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.45,0:11:00.83,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}Idola's daemons.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.06,0:11:03.14,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hunters.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.01,0:11:05.52,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.44,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}I lived as a soldier
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.98,0:11:09.91,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}in a world straight out of some LN.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.15,0:11:16.90,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a memory of fighting Gaia's mad dog.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.41,0:11:18.31,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the end,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.31,0:11:21.49,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}was it never possible for us \Nto come to an understanding?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.76,0:11:23.91,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, right.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.91,0:11:26.64,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}I even have a memory of racing down\N a highway at night with Shizuru,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.64,0:11:29.91,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}enacting a chase scene right out\N of a Hollywood blockbuster.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.38,0:11:35.04,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this is where the contradiction rears its ugly head.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.04,0:11:37.43,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}These memories are so inconsistent,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.43,0:11:39.67,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}they couldn't possibly be from the same life.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.02,0:11:42.27,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like I've been reborn countless times
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.27,0:11:44.65,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}and lived different lives each time.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.18,0:11:46.47,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's absurd.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.25,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I can't come up
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.25,0:11:51.81,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}with any other way to explain \Nmy inconsistent memories.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.81,0:11:55.85,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I stop racking my brain \Nand focus on the task ahead of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.32,0:11:57.57,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.57,0:12:00.82,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}the terrifying task of talking to this unshakable girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.19,0:12:03.07,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is something I must do.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.07,0:12:06.83,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because it's the only thing I have to cling to right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.67,0:12:08.50,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.95,0:12:14.76,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet, of course, I failed again.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.13,0:12:19.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,Man, I'm running out of things to say.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.82,0:12:24.43,Default,K,0,0,0,,Maybe I should just try a bolder method.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.13,0:12:29.01,Default,K,0,0,0,,Like attacking her or something.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.01,0:12:30.56,Default,K,0,0,0,,Nah, that won't do.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.56,0:12:33.80,Default,K,0,0,0,,Socializing calls for a friendlier approach...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.73,0:12:37.04,Default,K,0,0,0,,In terms of trying to attract her attention,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.04,0:12:38.90,Default,K,0,0,0,,isn't this just like hitting on a girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.64,0:12:41.78,Default,K,0,0,0,,I can't seem to get you off my mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.78,0:12:44.02,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'd make a great couple.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.02,0:12:47.07,Default,K,0,0,0,,So there's nothing to fear, baby.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.52,0:12:59.09,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.09,0:13:01.71,Default,K,0,0,0,,Why don't we start going out?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.81,0:13:05.97,Default,K,0,0,0,,My love is unstoppable!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.85,0:13:09.35,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}Je t'aime{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.81,0:13:13.06,Default,K,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.98,0:13:16.69,Default,K,0,0,0,,Play with adults, and you'll get burned.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.77,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm melting away!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.97,0:13:24.69,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm not getting anywhere!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.69,0:13:26.41,Default,K,0,0,0,,Killing me just for trying to approach her?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.41,0:13:29.12,Default,K,0,0,0,,This goes way beyond playing hard to get!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.12,0:13:32.35,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.63,0:13:37.83,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.83,0:13:39.48,Default,K,0,0,0,,Nothing's changed.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.48,0:13:42.71,Default,K,0,0,0,,Even here, everything I do is pointless.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.42,0:13:45.12,Default,K,0,0,0,,I just wanted somewhere to belong.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.62,0:13:47.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,I wanted to mean something to someone.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.14,0:13:50.69,Default,K,0,0,0,,I was scared of being left alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.69,0:13:51.79,Default,K,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.79,0:13:54.73,Default,K,0,0,0,,That's why I started the occult club, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.08,0:13:57.00,Default,K,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.44,0:13:58.78,Default,K,0,0,0,,Everyone's like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.78,0:14:01.73,Default,K,0,0,0,,So why have I been singled out \Nand hauled off here?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.09,0:14:03.66,Default,K,0,0,0,,Why am I the only one...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.96,0:14:06.34,Default,K,0,0,0,,in this god-forsaken place?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.85,0:14:10.69,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm a puny guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.32,0:14:12.76,Default,K,0,0,0,,Some small-time guy who tried
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.14,0:14:15.90,Default,K,0,0,0,,to get through life curled up \Ninto a tiny ball. That's all.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.90,0:14:16.80,Default,K,0,0,0,,So why...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.93,0:14:20.53,Default,K,0,0,0,,Why won't you leave me alone?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.46,0:14:26.35,Default,K,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.35,0:14:28.01,Default,K,0,0,0,,Kill me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.62,0:14:30.82,Default,K,0,0,0,,Help me not think about anything anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.48,0:14:32.82,Default,K,0,0,0,,Turn me back into nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.64,0:14:34.52,Default,K,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.61,0:14:40.59,Default,K,0,0,0,,What's your deal?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.59,0:14:42.27,Default,K,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.44,0:14:48.34,Default,K,0,0,0,,Did you...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.95,0:14:51.20,Default,K,0,0,0,,just say "Kagari"?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.56,0:14:54.03,Default,K,0,0,0,,K-Kagari?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.79,0:14:58.85,Default,K,0,0,0,,I-I've been wanting to ask.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.85,0:15:00.54,Default,K,0,0,0,,Have you always been alone?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.87,0:15:04.99,Default,K,0,0,0,,And, although I don't remember it,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.99,0:15:07.62,Default,K,0,0,0,,we've met before, haven't we?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.62,0:15:09.80,Default,K,0,0,0,,And not just once or twice, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.12,0:15:13.79,Default,K,0,0,0,,I don't know if I should call you \Na hard worker or what...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.79,0:15:16.08,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I know it's a bit late to ask,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.08,0:15:17.31,Default,K,0,0,0,,but what is this thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.07,0:15:27.16,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.16,0:15:28.35,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}A theory?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.35,0:15:30.51,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}This whole thing was
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.51,0:15:34.32,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}a super-dense mass of information?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.96,0:15:49.47,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this a theory of life?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.66,0:15:55.97,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}There were battles revolving around the Key.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.97,0:15:59.44,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}I took part in those battles, at times as part of Gaia,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.44,0:16:00.96,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}at times as a member of Guardian,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.96,0:16:01.98,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}and at times as...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.98,0:16:05.22,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}Some considered the Key Earth's messenger,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.22,0:16:07.19,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}sent to punish humanity for its hubris,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.19,0:16:10.05,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}and some considered her Earth's immune system.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.61,0:16:11.99,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}But in the end,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.59,0:16:16.99,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}everyone perished without learning\N anything about the Key.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.73,0:16:21.56,Default,K,0,0,0,,Are you researching a way to destroy the world?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.71,0:16:25.00,Default,K,0,0,0,,Humanity ruined the environment too much,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.00,0:16:27.00,Default,K,0,0,0,,so you're going to destroy it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.02,0:16:31.21,Default,K,0,0,0,,Figures.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.53,0:16:51.87,Default,K,0,0,0,,Kotori?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.95,0:16:53.89,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.97,0:16:57.74,Default,K,0,0,0,,All by yourself in such a lonely place again?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.38,0:17:06.92,Default,K,0,0,0,,Akane-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.36,Default,K,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.43,Default,K,0,0,0,,Looking awfully thin there.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.64,0:17:22.68,Default,K,0,0,0,,Lucia?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.38,0:17:32.07,Default,K,0,0,0,,Did she run away?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.45,0:17:33.58,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.58,0:17:36.57,Default,K,0,0,0,,I can't touch her unless it's through a cloth.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.14,0:17:40.16,Default,K,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.58,0:17:46.33,Default,K,0,0,0,,There's no fish or charcoal to use it with.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.44,0:17:54.09,Default,K,0,0,0,,You're always such a nice girl, Shizuru.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.59,0:18:00.35,Default,K,0,0,0,,This place is way too big for just two people.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.83,0:18:09.98,Default,K,0,0,0,,This is all she had, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.74,0:18:20.09,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought this town was deserted,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.52,0:18:21.99,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.99,0:18:26.00,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those were signs and vestiges of life.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.00,0:18:31.00,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}I bet it's all connected somehow.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.68,0:18:47.46,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}After that, I got killed countless times,\N and gained in return
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.46,0:18:49.27,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}this comfortable distance between us.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.63,0:18:51.81,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}I actually quite like it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.81,0:18:54.90,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, since we can't communicate,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.90,0:18:58.33,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}there are no lies or lip service in this relationship.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.75,0:19:02.78,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a completely pure connection\N I built with my own hands.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.43,0:19:09.29,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems Kagari's research \Nisn't proceeding too smoothly.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.92,0:19:12.00,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is there anything I can do to help?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.94,0:19:26.68,Default,K,0,0,0,,Why don't you take a break?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.22,0:19:36.19,Default,K,0,0,0,,It's good!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.20,0:19:51.28,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm a human, not a tree!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.79,0:19:56.36,Default,K,0,0,0,,Crap, I spaced out for months!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.34,0:20:03.19,Default,K,0,0,0,,Did your research hit a brick wall again?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.18,0:20:10.38,Default,K,0,0,0,,Uh, here you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.19,0:20:31.88,Default,Kag,0,0,0,,I don't actually want to drink this muddy water,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.88,0:20:33.58,Default,Kag,0,0,0,,but you left me no choice!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.95,0:20:35.16,Default,K,0,0,0,,As if.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.48,0:20:39.19,Default,K,0,0,0,,Uh, are you...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.80,0:20:44.22,Default,K,0,0,0,,You weren't asking for seconds, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.50,0:20:49.30,Default,Kag,0,0,0,,Trying to win me over with a drink like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.30,0:20:52.02,Default,Kag,0,0,0,,I suppose that's the best an inferior\N human could hope to think of.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.02,0:20:53.52,Default,K,0,0,0,,As if.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.52,0:21:01.28,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet again, time passes without feeling like it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.98,0:21:13.29,Default,K,0,0,0,,I-I'll make some right away!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.27,0:21:30.80,Default,K,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.95,0:21:48.07,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}Welp, I'm dead again.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.57,0:22:01.53,Default,K,0,0,0,,Kagari?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.06,0:22:04.20,Default,K,0,0,0,,A-Are you sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.64,0:22:10.35,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you telling me...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.92,0:22:13.00,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}three cups of coffee was all it took
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.00,0:22:15.85,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}to break down the final barrier between us?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.89,0:22:20.84,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're not friends,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.84,0:22:22.15,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}lovers,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.15,0:22:24.11,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}family, or anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.72,0:22:25.94,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forget all that.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.34,0:22:28.33,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can't even talk to each other.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:29.40,0:22:30.37,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.20,0:22:35.32,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though it's so thin that \Nit could snap at any moment,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.87,0:22:37.87,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}there was something that connected us.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.00,0:22:43.50,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've found my answer.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.16,0:22:48.08,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wouldn't mind risking my life for this right here!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.34,0:23:07.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right, Kagari...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:07.72,0:23:08.80,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}You never were...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.06,0:23:13.03,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}some incomprehensible being!
